{"tid":1089973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"洗碗碟機短路起火 高翔苑單位寵物狗慘死","createTime":"2019-04-03T06:53:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T16:02:41.000Z","uid":3090,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bafa80b850d6263e2f5357fe70145186ef84f2b9","tid":1089973,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T06:53:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5nSAf6Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5nSAf6Y.png&h=64db2ba0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n油塘高翔苑高康閣一個單位中午發生火警。劉永明攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3C30sdL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3C30sdL.png&h=d6cdb6b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n油塘高翔苑高康閣一個單位中午發生火警。劉永明攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yJPGbFx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyJPGbFx.png&h=2fef75cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o7rmbFP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo7rmbFP.png&h=f6edf53c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n愛協曾經到場了解。劉永明攝<br />\n<br />\n油塘高翔苑高康閣一個單位中午12時半發生火警，火勢猛烈，單位外牆被熏黑，消防員到場破門入屋，開喉灌救，並疏散住客至地上安全位置，火警迅速被救熄，無人受傷，但單位內一隻狗慘被燒死。<br />\n<br />\n起火大廈為紀律部隊宿舍，火警發生時單位內空無一人，經調查後初步相信因洗碗碟機短路引起。警方稍後聯絡到男戶主，趕回善後及處理狗屍。"},{"pid":"0cc4ca436663b4fd672b25b147bbc6d1828fa123","tid":1089973,"uid":40272,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T06:54:59.000Z","msg":"神仙企唔穩"},{"pid":"89ac1e825d0abb7442cb183525ee24b520203773","tid":1089973,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T07:37:05.000Z","msg":"中國製？"},{"pid":"3d43fd89b177e9a4fada9047ea5cfb8830be4e75","tid":1089973,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"89ac1e825d0abb7442cb183525ee24b520203773","tid":1089973,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T07:37:05.000Z","msg":"中國製？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T08:02:47.000Z","msg":"未必，如果特登買洗碗碟機一定有米"},